<section aria-label="Advisory disclosure" class="bg-soft py-10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8" data-animate="fade-up">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:gap-5">
      <div class="grid h-10 w-10 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-medical/10 text-medical">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
          <path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
        <div class="font-semibold text-navy">We are an independent advisory service.</div>
        <p class="mt-1.5">
          We do not provide dental treatment directly. We connect international patients with vetted, licensed dental clinics in Cyprus.
          All clinical care, treatment planning and pricing are delivered by the partner clinic, with whom you will contract directly.
          Our advisory service is free for patients — you pay the clinic the same price as walking in independently.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
